<BLOCKQUOTE>
<HR>
Sunlei wrote:<BR>
<DIV>&nbsp;Everyone who attends the event should roll on loot with the GM running the rolls.&nbsp; </DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>A person wins something and that's the end of event for them, the GM needs to be in charge of loot and rolls.</DIV>
